No. 09-10885. Louis Robenson, Petitioner v. R. J. Bonshall, et al. 562 U.S. 803, 131 S. Ct. 117,

178 L. Ed. 2d 4,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7729. October 4, 2010.

Motion of petitioners for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari *5to the Supreme Court of Florida dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 29 So. 3d 291.
